<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<definitions xmlns="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/MODEL" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:activiti="http://activiti.org/bpmn" xmlns:bpmndi="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/DI" xmlns:omgdc="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DC" xmlns:omgdi="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DI" typeLanguage="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" expressionLanguage="http://www.w3.org/1999/XPath" targetNamespace="point.io">
  <message id="documentApprovalMsg" name="documentApprovalMsg"></message>
  <message id="testquick" name="testquick"></message>
  <message id="injectListJSON" name="injectListJSON"></message>
  <collaboration id="Collaboration">
    <participant id="pool1" name="Pool" processRef="process_pool1"></participant>
  </collaboration>
  <process id="approval" name="Approval" isExecutable="true">
    <laneSet id="laneSet_process_pool1">
      <lane id="system" name="System">
        <flowNodeRef>start</flowNodeRef>
        <flowNodeRef>exclusivegateway3</flowNodeRef>
        <flowNodeRef>setOriginator</flowNodeRef>
        <flowNodeRef>servicetask1</flowNodeRef>
        <flowNodeRef>getToBeSelected</flowNodeRef>
        <flowNodeRef>addPartyServiceTask</flowNodeRef>
        <flowNodeRef>listToBeApproved</flowNodeRef>
        <flowNodeRef>mailtask1</flowNodeRef>
        <flowNodeRef>messagestartevent1</flowNodeRef>
        <flowNodeRef>exclusivegateway4</flowNodeRef>
      </lane>
      <lane id="requestor" name="Requestor">
        <flowNodeRef>addParties</flowNodeRef>
        <flowNodeRef>end</flowNodeRef>
        <flowNodeRef>end</flowNodeRef>
      </lane>
      <lane id="approver" name="Approver">
        <flowNodeRef>documentApprovalTrigger</flowNodeRef>
        <flowNodeRef>ApproveReject</flowNodeRef>
        <flowNodeRef>inclusivegateway1</flowNodeRef>
      </lane>
    </laneSet>
    <startEvent id="start" name="Start Review" activiti:formKey="wf:submitReviewTask"></startEvent>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow1" sourceRef="start" targetRef="exclusivegateway3"></sequenceFlow>
    <exclusiveGateway id="exclusivegateway3" name="Exclusive Gateway"></exclusiveGateway>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow34" sourceRef="exclusivegateway3" targetRef="setOriginator">
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression"><![CDATA[${wf_currentAssignee == ""}]]></conditionExpression>
    </sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow36" sourceRef="exclusivegateway3" targetRef="servicetask1"></sequenceFlow>
    <serviceTask id="setOriginator" name="Set Originator" activiti:class="plugins.wf_Loop_Role">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="roleName">
          <activiti:string><![CDATA["Originator"]]></activiti:string>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow32" sourceRef="setOriginator" targetRef="getToBeSelected"></sequenceFlow>
    <serviceTask id="servicetask1" name="Set First Assignee" activiti:expression="#{execution.setVariable("Originator_LIST", wf_currentAssignee)} #{execution.setVariable("Originator_COUNT", 1)} #{execution.setVariable("Originator_LOOP", 0)}"></serviceTask>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow37" sourceRef="servicetask1" targetRef="getToBeSelected"></sequenceFlow>
    <serviceTask id="getToBeSelected" name="To-Be Selected" activiti:class="plugins.facts">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="PluginKey">
          <activiti:string><![CDATA[poi_listtobe_fact]]></activiti:string>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="parameterMap">
          <activiti:expression>${listMap}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow47" sourceRef="getToBeSelected" targetRef="addParties"></sequenceFlow>
    <serviceTask id="addPartyServiceTask" name="Set Parties Manual" activiti:class="plugins.wf_Add_Parties"></serviceTask>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow30" name="add more" sourceRef="exclusivegateway4" targetRef="addParties">
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression"><![CDATA[${wf_optionsOutcome == "addmore"}]]></conditionExpression>
    </sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow31" name="cancel" sourceRef="exclusivegateway4" targetRef="end">
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression"><![CDATA[${wf_optionsOutcome == "cancel"}]]></conditionExpression>
    </sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow38" name="continue" sourceRef="exclusivegateway4" targetRef="listToBeApproved"></sequenceFlow>
    <serviceTask id="listToBeApproved" name="To-Be Approved" activiti:class="plugins.facts">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="PluginKey">
          <activiti:string><![CDATA[poi_gettobe_fact]]></activiti:string>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="parameterMap">
          <activiti:expression>${getMap}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow51" sourceRef="listToBeApproved" targetRef="ApproveReject"></sequenceFlow>
    <serviceTask id="mailtask1" name="Notify Final" activiti:type="mail">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="to">
          <activiti:expression>${Respondee_LIST}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="from">
          <activiti:string><![CDATA[alert@point.io]]></activiti:string>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="subject">
          <activiti:expression>You are being notified that the Process ${execution.getProcessInstanceId()} has completed.</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="html">
          <activiti:expression><p>Process ${execution.getProcessInstanceId()} started by ${Originator_LIST} has completed.</p>
<p>
<table>
<tr><td>Approvers:</td><td>${Approver_LIST}</td></tr>
<tr><td>CC:</td><td>${Originator_LIST}</td></tr>
</table>
</p></activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="cc">
          <activiti:expression>${Originator_LIST}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow26" sourceRef="mailtask1" targetRef="end"></sequenceFlow>
    <startEvent id="messagestartevent1" name="Message start">
      <messageEventDefinition messageRef="testquick"></messageEventDefinition>
    </startEvent>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow46" sourceRef="messagestartevent1" targetRef="mailtask1"></sequenceFlow>
    <startEvent id="documentApprovalTrigger" name="documentApprovalTrigger">
      <messageEventDefinition messageRef="documentApprovalMsg"></messageEventDefinition>
    </startEvent>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow44" sourceRef="documentApprovalTrigger" targetRef="ApproveReject"></sequenceFlow>
    <subProcess id="ApproveReject" name="ApproveReject">
      <multiInstanceLoopCharacteristics isSequential="false" activiti:collection="Approver_LIST_COL" activiti:elementVariable="assignee"></multiInstanceLoopCharacteristics>
      <userTask id="review" name="Review Request" activiti:assignee="${assignee}" activiti:formKey="poi_review_form">
        <documentation>Review associated documentation and Approve/Reject.</documentation>
        <extensionElements>
          <activiti:formProperty id="wf_optionsOutcome" name="Options" type="enum" required="true">
            <activiti:value id="approve" name="Approve"></activiti:value>
            <activiti:value id="reject" name="Reject"></activiti:value>
          </activiti:formProperty>
        </extensionElements>
      </userTask>
      <sequenceFlow id="flow27" sourceRef="review" targetRef="reviewDecision"></sequenceFlow>
      <exclusiveGateway id="reviewDecision" name="Approve or Reject?"></exclusiveGateway>
      <sequenceFlow id="flowapprove" name="approved" sourceRef="reviewDecision" targetRef="approveMail">
        <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression"><![CDATA[${wf_optionsOutcome == 'approve'}]]></conditionExpression>
      </sequenceFlow>
      <sequenceFlow id="flowreject" name="rejected" sourceRef="reviewDecision" targetRef="selectReason">
        <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression"><![CDATA[${wf_optionsOutcome == 'reject'}]]></conditionExpression>
      </sequenceFlow>
      <serviceTask id="approveMail" name="Approved Mail" activiti:type="mail">
        <extensionElements>
          <activiti:field name="to">
            <activiti:expression>${Originator_LIST}</activiti:expression>
          </activiti:field>
          <activiti:field name="from">
            <activiti:string><![CDATA[alert@point.io]]></activiti:string>
          </activiti:field>
          <activiti:field name="subject">
            <activiti:expression>Request ${execution.getProcessInstanceId()} is Approved!</activiti:expression>
          </activiti:field>
          <activiti:field name="html">
            <activiti:expression>Your request id ${execution.getProcessInstanceId()} has been reviewed and approved by ${assignee}.</activiti:expression>
          </activiti:field>
        </extensionElements>
      </serviceTask>
      <userTask id="selectReason" name="Select Failure Reason" activiti:assignee="${assignee}" activiti:formKey="poi_reject_form">
        <documentation>Select reason for Rejection.</documentation>
        <extensionElements>
          <activiti:formProperty id="wf_optionsOutcome" name="Rejection Reason" type="enum" required="true">
            <activiti:value id="outofpolicy" name="Out of Policy"></activiti:value>
            <activiti:value id="duplicate" name="Duplicate Request"></activiti:value>
            <activiti:value id="invalid" name="Invalid Request"></activiti:value>
            <activiti:value id="other" name="Other"></activiti:value>
          </activiti:formProperty>
        </extensionElements>
      </userTask>
      <serviceTask id="rejectMail" name="Rejected Mail" activiti:type="mail">
        <extensionElements>
          <activiti:field name="to">
            <activiti:expression>${Originator_LIST}</activiti:expression>
          </activiti:field>
          <activiti:field name="from">
            <activiti:string><![CDATA[alert@point.io]]></activiti:string>
          </activiti:field>
          <activiti:field name="subject">
            <activiti:expression>Request ${execution.getProcessInstanceId()} Rejected</activiti:expression>
          </activiti:field>
          <activiti:field name="html">
            <activiti:expression>Your request id ${execution.getProcessInstanceId()} has been reviewed and rejected by ${assignee}.</activiti:expression>
          </activiti:field>
        </extensionElements>
      </serviceTask>
      <endEvent id="endevent1" name="End SubFlow Review"></endEvent>
      <sequenceFlow id="flow39" sourceRef="approveMail" targetRef="endevent1"></sequenceFlow>
      <sequenceFlow id="flow40" sourceRef="rejectMail" targetRef="endevent1"></sequenceFlow>
      <startEvent id="startevent1" name="Start SubFlow Review"></startEvent>
      <sequenceFlow id="flow45" sourceRef="startevent1" targetRef="review"></sequenceFlow>
      <sequenceFlow id="flow52" sourceRef="selectReason" targetRef="rejectMail"></sequenceFlow>
    </subProcess>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow41" sourceRef="ApproveReject" targetRef="inclusivegateway1"></sequenceFlow>
    <inclusiveGateway id="inclusivegateway1" name="Inclusive Gateway"></inclusiveGateway>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow42" sourceRef="inclusivegateway1" targetRef="mailtask1"></sequenceFlow>
    <userTask id="addParties" name="Select Parties &  Records" activiti:assignee="${wf_currentAssignee}">

          <activiti:value id="Approver" name="Approver"></activiti:value>
          <activiti:value id="Respondee" name="Respondee"></activiti:value>
        </activiti:formProperty>
        <activiti:formProperty id="party1_email" name="Party 1 Email" type="string"></activiti:formProperty>
        <activiti:formProperty id="party2_role" name="Party 2 Role" type="enum">
          <activiti:value id="Approver" name="Approver"></activiti:value>
          <activiti:value id="Respondee" name="Respondee"></activiti:value>
        </activiti:formProperty>
        <activiti:formProperty id="party2_email" name="Party 2 Email" type="string"></activiti:formProperty>
        <activiti:formProperty id="party3_role" name="Party 3 Role" type="enum">
          <activiti:value id="Approver" name="Approver"></activiti:value>
          <activiti:value id="Respondee" name="Respondee"></activiti:value>
        </activiti:formProperty>
        <activiti:formProperty id="party3_email" name="Party 3 Email" type="string"></activiti:formProperty>
        <activiti:formProperty id="wf_optionsOutcome" name="Option Selection" type="enum" required="true">
          <activiti:value id="continue" name="Continue"></activiti:value>
          <activiti:value id="addmore" name="Add More Parties"></activiti:value>
          <activiti:value id="cancel" name="Cancel"></activiti:value>
        </activiti:formProperty>
      </extensionElements>
    </userTask>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow28" sourceRef="addParties" targetRef="addPartyServiceTask"></sequenceFlow>
    <endEvent id="end" name="End Review"></endEvent>
    <exclusiveGateway id="exclusivegateway4" name="Exclusive Gateway"></exclusiveGateway>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow53" sourceRef="addPartyServiceTask" targetRef="exclusivegateway4"></sequenceFlow>
    <boundaryEvent id="addPartiesMessage" name="Message" attachedToRef="addParties" cancelActivity="false">
      <messageEventDefinition messageRef="injectListJSON"></messageEventDefinition>
    </boundaryEvent>
  </process>
